      "problem": "Consider the quadratic equation x^2 - 8x + 16 = 0. What is the sum of the reciprocals of its roots?",
      "answer": "0.5",
      "source_code": "import random\n\nCONCEPT_TYPE = \"algebra.quadratic_vieta_reciprocal\"\nCONCEPT_GROUP = \"algebra\"\n\ndef generate(seed):\n    rng = random.Random(seed)\n\n    a = rng.randint(1, 5)\n    b = rng.randint(1, 5)\n    c = rng.randint(1, 5)\n\n    # Given a quadratic equation x^2 - (a+b)x + ab = 0,\n    # the sum of reciprocals of its roots is (a+b)/ab.\n    sum_of_reciprocals = (a + b) / (a * b)\n\n    problem = (\n        f\"Consider the quadratic equation x^2 - {a+b}x + {a*b} = 0. \"\n        f\"What is the sum of the reciprocals of its roots?\"\n    )\n\n    return problem, str(sum_of_reciprocals)"
